    "This approach is particularly effective in ensuring high precision in responses.",
    "Graph RAG, on the other hand, leverages structured relationships in knowledge graphs to guide retrieval and contextualize information, enabling the system to answer complex queries that require understanding entity relationships and dependencies.",
    "These variations highlight the versatility of RAG frameworks in addressing diverse information needs.",
    "Despite its strengths, RAG can face challenges when semantically similar yet contextually irrelevant chunks are retrieved.",
    "This highlights the importance of refinement techniques to align retrieved data with user intent."
